metadata.name: Two Under The Moonlight
metadata.description:
This work tries to convey the mood of variability. Different situations make us experience a sharp contrast of emotions, is under the spotlight and humbly accept the burden of circumstances. Wholeness in opposites is like Yin Yang. But do not forget that we are all just dummies in the incomprehensible hands of fate.

First piece from the "Fantastic Creatures" collection.
Original Dimensions: 4320 x 2700.

Created with Blender, Cycles / Marvelous / Mixamo.
